parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiShOpNo1.This is what I saw! This was in my dream!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Damn! This place is bigger than I thought.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoOp.Creepy… What the hell are these statues?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.This stone here… It’s part of the Toma Leolo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The Toma… It’s a magic rock… It’s part of a Casula idol.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.Casula? Judging from the symbol on the floor I’d say this is more along the lines of Christian demonic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t know how it connects, but I have three other pieces of this statue…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaDe.Just what type of effects are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I’m serious. The last one I found made my dick bigger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoCl.But the feeling… I felt so horny.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I felt it too… It must be the stone doing it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaAg.This is amazing! The magic rocks, the satanic cult hideout… This will give us content for years!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.You’re really going to report on magic sex rocks?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Something’s up and we’re going to break the story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Fuck. Let’s get out of here before more of them show up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnDe.Mother may trust you, but I do not.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Take him to the rift. I will be there shortly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOpNo1.Kimberly!? What are you doing down here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaAg.I know so much now, 1Hero! What a story!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Where is Lillian? What did you see?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaEx.There’s a portal to another world! And I’m going to break the story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp^.An unfortunate turn of events, but do not fret…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx^.Once you complete the Toma, we will have all we need to bring peace.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp.How much more time do you need, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx^.We will stay hidden until you’ve completed the statue… Then salvation can come to the worlds of chaos.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Kimberly, the Guild bust is happening today!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoOp.Shit… I need to get back to the office… I need to prepare.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx^.Miss Foxx… You are going to show the world something they’ve never imagined in their wildest dreams.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No offense, but this is all kinda hard to believe… You’ll look crazy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx^.Don’t listen to that. The people are ready to know the truth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.Of course… They need to know the truth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.You have to help me, Kimberly. If you don’t, Nellie will go to jail and Melissa will lose her job.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx^.Do what you must, but between the two of you I expect the Toma Leolo to be completed…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnEx.Let me help. I can help find the Toma pieces.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx^.Absolutely not. You must remain hidden. We must buy 1Hero time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnExNo1.Our time is coming to an end. Do not fail Mother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoOp.Can we get out of here without getting spotted by the police?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiShOpNo1^.Oh, my Lord! What is she doing down here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoEx^.There are men taking over the mansion, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.What’s going on, Lillian? You’re working with Madalyn and she’s working with Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoCl^.I… I don’t know what you’re talking about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.The Toma pieces… They are all here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoEx^.We must combine the pieces, 1Hero. Our lives are at stake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiMaAgNo1^.No one’s supposed to be down here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx^.You want to escape this mansion? Then let’s complete the Toma–now!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.How the hell do you expect us to do that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx^.Do not worry, my dear. We simply require your… special ancestry…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.What are you going to do to Erica?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx^.I’m not going to do anything to her…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoClNo1^.Argh! How the hell did you get down here!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiMaAgNo1>.If you want me, come and get me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoEx>.We have to get out of here before Duncan realizes we’re gone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeShOp.What the hell are you doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Take them. Let’s get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoMaAgNo1^.You will not take the Toma Leolo from us!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnOp.About damn time. What took you so long?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.We split up. Tasha and I will handle Madalyn… Those goons upstairs are more of a target for the adventurers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.So… They are going to kill Duncan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.How do we get into the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I know how to activate it. I’ll meet you there…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.You’ll know it when you see it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Come on, Tasha. Stay close to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Shit… Get dressed. We need to find Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She got away! She has the Toma!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx^.The priest told me you’d be having a party down here. I didn’t believe him at first.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.There’s no time to waste. We need to go to the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.We should listen to him… The Wilkes’ daughter and her minions escaped through here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Not the bunker. It attaches to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx^.It must be that Daemalius creature. It’s angry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaWoCl^.I don’t want to die like this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnEx.Suck it up! We’re here to do a mission.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Father… Here is the demon part… Open the rift.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We’re not far from the entry. I’ll bring the girls back to the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoCl^.We need to get back to the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Let’s leave before that lightning storm returns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAgNo1.I don’t care what you say, I’m getting my army!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAg.The Guild will be bigger and better than ever!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx>.Duncan, the Toma Leolo was destroyed. It’s over. Put the gun down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAgNo1.No! I don’t believe it! It can be put back together!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnEx>.You’re crazy! Can’t you see? What’s left?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAg.Take one step and this officer is dead!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It’s over, Dad. You need to put the gun down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAgNo1!a.You arrogant whelp! I’ll put the gun down when I want to!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx^.I’m sorry, Nellie, but you’re also under arrest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdWoEx^.Bobby, it wasn’t her fault. She didn’t know what she was doing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeSaEx.Calm down, Tasha… I’m not escaping this one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OcBaEx.Detective Canmore, we have to bring you in, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Don’t worry… We’ll get him out of this… somehow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "OcAnDe.What about her? You have a permit for that gun, miss?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObWoEx^.She saved us… That’s not her gun.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoCl>.I think it might be time to scram.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErMaAgNo1.What kind of happy ending is this? How dare you arrest the good guys!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnEx^.Use some common sense! 1Hero’s not a bad man!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx^.This isn’t over… We’ll have our trial.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAgNo1.You’ll pay for this! All of you will!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Don’t worry… I have a feeling things will work out just fine.");
